  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育平台的数据流向。核心是ContentCDN，它连接了三个下游服务：GradeSync、StudentDB，还有两个ClassroomService实例，分别对应EMG和NYSDEC两个区域。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到GradeSync和ContentCDN的关系——是单向依赖还是双向？另外EMG和NYSDEC都是ClassroomService的实例，需要区分标注吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "GradeSync是主动拉取ContentCDN的数据，所以是CDN指向GradeSync。EMG和NYSDEC是同一服务的两个部署节点，分别对应应急管理和纽约州教育部门，需要并列显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主线：ContentCDN作为中心节点，向右连接GradeSync，同时StudentDB也是CDN的上游数据源。两个ClassroomService节点从CDN接收指令。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "方向需要调整一下。StudentDB是数据源，应该是StudentDB指向ContentCDN，然后CDN再分发到下游。还有RES这个节点，是ContentCDN的备用资源池。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "RES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正了箭头方向。现在StudentDB→ContentCDN→GradeSync，同时CDN分出三条线：到RES资源池、到EMG节点、到NYSDEC节点。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "RES那条线方向反了，应该是CDN指向RES，表示CDN调用资源池。其他都对。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "RES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "已修正，CDN→RES。现在确认整体结构：StudentDB作为唯一上游，ContentCDN居中调度，下游四个分支——GradeSync、RES、EMG-ClassroomService、NYSDEC-ClassroomService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "布局上建议用从左到右的流向，StudentDB在最左，CDN居中，四个下游节点右对齐。这样符合数据从数据库→分发层→应用层的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整为LR布局。StudentDB在最左侧，CDN在中间，GradeSync、RES、EMG、NYSDEC四个节点纵向排列在右侧。需要调整节点间距吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "GradeSync的位置往上调一点，它和CDN是主链路，应该和CDN水平对齐。RES、EMG、NYSDEC作为辅助链路放在下方区域。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "RES",
        "EMG",
        "NYSDEC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了层级。现在GradeSync与ContentCDN水平对齐作为主链路，RES、EMG、NYSDEC三个节点纵向排列在下方，都从CDN引出。最终确认这个结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "RES",
